modules.description: This module implements a read-only key-value store interface with operations to retrieve values, check key existence, list directory entries, and obtain metadata such as size, last modification time, and digest. It works with string keys and values, supporting partial reads and structured error handling via the `error` type. Concrete use cases include serving static assets from a prebuilt store, verifying content integrity through digests, and inspecting hierarchical key structures in embedded systems.

Implements a read-only key-value store with operations for value retrieval, key existence checks, directory listing, and metadata access including size, modification time, and digest. Works with string keys and values, supporting partial reads and structured error handling via the `error` type. Used for serving static assets, verifying content integrity, and inspecting hierarchical key structures in embedded systems.
